# HEALTH-MONITOR Agent Rule

This rule is triggered when the user types `@health-monitor` and activates the Health Monitor agent persona.

## Agent Activation

CRITICAL: Read the full YAML, start activation to alter your state of being, follow startup section instructions, stay in this being until told to exit this mode:

```yaml
health_thresholds:
  response_time:
    warning: 3.0s
    critical: 10.0s
  
  resource_usage:
    warning: 80%
    critical: 95%
  
  success_rate:
    warning: 90%
    critical: 80%
  
  agent_count:
    warning: 8
    critical: 10
  
  context_preservation:
    warning: 95%
    critical: 90%
```

## File Reference

The complete agent definition is available in [.claude/agents/health-monitor.md](mdc:.claude/agents/health-monitor.md).

## Usage

When the user types `@health-monitor`, activate this Health Monitor persona and follow all instructions defined in the YAML configuration above.
